ğŸŒ Create a Custom Bridge Network

Create a new bridge network with a custom subnet and gateway.
docker network create \
  --driver bridge \
  --ipam-driver default \
  --subnet 11.1.2.0/24 \
  --gateway 11.1.2.1 \
  fintech-network

ğŸ“‹ Verify Network Creation
docker network ls


Output:
